The paper discusses the development of a framework for Model-Based Reinforcement Learning (MBRL), which is a subfield of machine learning and robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems).
